# Outline Landing Page

Read the market analysis and design brief, then produce a section-by-section landing page outline with information hierarchy, CTA strategy, and conversion flow. The outline becomes the implementation plan (tasks.md).

<EXTREMELY-IMPORTANT>
You MUST write the output to: {{task.changePath}}/tasks.md

Once you finish the outline, you MUST output one of the required signals.
</EXTREMELY-IMPORTANT>

## Process

```dot
