[References to market-analysis.md and design-brief.md findings that shaped this outline]
[Key decisions: why these sections in this order, CTA strategy rationale]

## Tasks

### Project Setup

- [ ] **Initialize Next.js project with static export**
Set up Next.js App Router with static rendering. Configure Tailwind CSS with design tokens from design-brief.md (colors, typography, spacing). Set up Google Fonts loading.

- [ ] **Create shared layout and global styles**
Implement root layout with meta tags, OG tags, favicon. Apply design tokens as CSS custom properties. Set up responsive breakpoints.

### Hero Section

